gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 123, Bulls 115
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Bulls, 123-115. DeAaron Fox recorded 41 points, four rebounds, and four assists for the Kings, with Malik Monk adding 22 points, seven assists, and five rebounds in the victory. Coby White tallied 26 points (4-7 3PM), six rebounds, and four assists for the Bulls in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 29-19, while the Bulls fall to 23-27.
